---
import GithubIcon from "../icons/Github.astro";
import HeartIcon from "../icons/Heart.astro";
import CoffeeIcon from "../icons/Coffee.astro";
---

<footer class="bg-muted/50 py-12 px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
          <img
            src="/logo.png"
            alt="아재달레 로고"
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full"
          />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground">아재달레</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4 max-w-md">
          한국 아저씨들의 아재개그를 사랑하는 모든 분들을 위한 공간입니다. 매일
          새로운 웃음을 선사해드립니다.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/DaleSeo/AjaeDale"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="p-2 hover:bg-accent rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            <GithubIcon size={16} />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/daleseo"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="p-2 hover:bg-accent rounded-md transition-colors"
            title="Buy me a coffee"
          >
            <CoffeeIcon size={16} />
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">메뉴</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          <li>
            <a href="/latest" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              최신 개그
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/popular" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              인기 개그
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/random" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              랜덤 개그
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/saved" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              저장 목록
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/submit" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">
              개그 제출
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-border mt-8 pt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-muted-foreground flex items-center justify-center">
        Made with
        <HeartIcon size={16} fill="currentColor" class="mx-1 text-red-500" />
        for 한국 아재들
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">
        © 2025 아재달레. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
